  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The UK Government in Wales hosted a live virtual event on Thursday 12 November to help Welsh businesses prepare for the end of the Transition Period</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
